Entity_ID: 1. Entity_ID: Unique identifier for each entity - use consistent format
2. Country_Code: Use ISO 3166-1 Alpha-2 codes (GB UK DE FR etc)
3. TIN: Enter NOTIN if no TIN issued by jurisdiction
4. GloBE_Status: UPE/CE/PE/JV/Excluded - per GloBE rules classification
5. Ownership_Pct: Direct ownership by immediate parent (decimal format 0-100)
6. UPE_Ownership_Pct: Ultimate ownership through chain to UPE
10. Update Last_Updated and Updated_By when making changes
